<div id="about-the-community" class="section-spacer">
    <h2 class="sect-title">About Rocky Ridge</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">Rocky Ridge real estate was first established 1998 after its annexation to Calgary in 1989. The neighborhood is represented by the Ward 1 Councilor at the Calgary City Council.</p>
            <p class="par-xl">Rocky Ridge homes for sale fetch good prices mainly due to the overall location of the area. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">Due to its elevated positioning (1,265 meters), residents get to enjoy splendid views of the surrounding locations.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">Rocky Ridge is located on the western extreme of the city with Country Hills Boulevard bordering it on the northern side and the Crowchild Trail bordering its southern side.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">The eastern and western sides are bordered by Rocky Ridge Road and Twelve Mile Coulee Road, respectively.</p>
        </div>
